1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about antibiotic spectrum than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:09,600
Antibiotic spectrum refers to the range of bacteria an antibiotic can affect.

3
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:14,800
Broad-spectrum antibiotics target many bacteria, but narrow-spectrum ones zero in on specific types.

4
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:16,400
Why does it matter?

5
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:19,200
Overusing broad-spectrum antibiotics can lead to resistance.

6
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:22,400
This could make future infections harder to treat.

7
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:25,600
Understanding antibiotic spectrum helps us use them wisely.

8
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:27,600
It’s about preserving their power.

9
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:30,000
Stay informed and share this knowledge!

10
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Follow for more science insights.
